@startuml
!theme plain

title agents-infra Primary Codex Session Resolution

|agents-infra discovery|
start
:Walk ancestor directories root to leaf;
:Parse each .agents/.configs/project-config.toml;
if (Any invalid file?) then (yes)
  :Return path + field error;
  stop
endif
:Compose model, effort, yolo per field;
note right
  Nearest present value wins.
  Explicit false overrides inherited true.
end note

|CLI normalizer|
:Parse wrapper and explicit Codex arguments;
if (Conflicting explicit value?) then (yes)
  :Fail before exec;
  stop
endif
if (Explicit --profile?) then (yes)
  :Suppress project model and effort;
else (no)
  :Fill unpinned model/effort from project;
endif
:Leave remaining dimensions Codex-native;

if (Explicit yolo or effective yolo=true?) then (yes)
  :Emit exactly one native dangerous flag;
else (no)
  :Emit no dangerous flag;
endif

|Evidence or launch|
if (--print-config?) then (yes)
  :Render values, provenance, suppression, argv;
  stop
endif
:Launch Codex with final argv;
stop

@enduml
